# Perplexity/Claude SaaS Project - Visual TLDR

This file is the quick visual guide for understanding the whole project.

Goal:
Build a real SaaS AI answer engine:

```txt
Login user
  -> ask question
  -> search web
  -> scrape sources
  -> generate cited AI answer
  -> stream answer live
  -> save chat history
  -> show library/settings/billing later
```

===============================================================================
1. ONE-LINE PROJECT MAP
===============================================================================

```txt
Frontend React/Vite
  |
  | calls APIs
  v
Backend Express
  |
  +-> MongoDB stores users/chats/messages/sources
  +-> Tavily/Brave/Exa searches web
  +-> Jina/Firecrawl extracts page content
  +-> Groq/OpenAI/Claude generates answer
  +-> Redis caches/rate-limits later
```

