```

===============================================================================
3. CORE FEATURE: ANSWER ENGINE WORKFLOW
===============================================================================

This is the most important workflow in the whole project.

```txt
User writes question
  |
  v
Frontend sends:
POST /api/search
{ query, mode, model, chatId }
  |
  v
Backend validates query
  |
  v
Optional query rewrite
"best laptop" -> "best laptops 2026 reviews performance battery"
  |
  v
Search web using Tavily/Brave/Exa
  |
  v
Get top URLs + titles + snippets
  |
  v
Scrape top URLs using Jina Reader/Firecrawl
  |
  v
Build numbered sources
[1] source A
[2] source B
[3] source C
  |
  v
Send prompt + source content to Groq/OpenAI/Claude
  |
  v
LLM returns answer with citations
"RAG combines retrieval and generation [1][2]."
  |
  v
Backend streams tokens to frontend using SSE
  |
  v
Frontend shows live answer + source cards
  |
  v
MongoDB saves chat, messages, sources
```

===============================================================================
4. BACKEND REQUEST PIPELINE DIAGRAM
===============================================================================

```txt
POST /api/search
      |
      v
+----------------------+
| search.routes.js     |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           v
+----------------------+
| search.controller.js |
+----------+-----------+
           |
           +--> search.validator.js
           |        checks query is valid
           |
           +--> usage.service.js
           |        checks free/pro usage limit
           |
           +--> queryRewrite.service.js
           |        improves search query
           |
           +--> search.service.js
           |        calls Tavily/Brave/Exa
           |
           +--> scraper.service.js
           |        calls Jina/Firecrawl
           |
           +--> citation.service.js
           |        numbers and validates sources
           |
           +--> groq.service.js
           |        generates AI answer
           |
           +--> stream.service.js
           |        streams tokens with SSE
           |
           +--> chat.service.js
                    saves chat/messages/sources
```

===============================================================================
5. FRONTEND WORKFLOW DIAGRAM
===============================================================================

```txt
Home.jsx
  |
  | user types query
  v
ChatInput.jsx
  |
  | on submit
  v
useChat.js
  |
  | calls API
  v
chat.api.js
  |
  | POST /api/search or /api/search/stream
  v
Backend
  |
  | returns sources + answer tokens
  v
useChat.js updates state
  |
  +--> ChatThread.jsx
  |      shows full conversation
  |
  +--> MessageBubble.jsx
  |      shows user/AI messages
  |
  +--> StreamingAnswer.jsx
  |      renders live AI answer
  |
  +--> CitationBadge.jsx
  |      turns [1] into clickable source badge
  |
  +--> SourcePanel.jsx
         shows sources on right side
```

