===============================================================================
12. EXTERNAL APIs YOU NEED
===============================================================================

```txt
AI / LLM:
  Groq first
  OpenAI optional
  Anthropic optional

Search:
  Tavily first
  Brave optional
  Exa optional

Scraping:
  Jina Reader first
  Firecrawl optional

Database:
  MongoDB Atlas

Cache / limits later:
  Redis

Email:
  Nodemailer + Gmail/SMTP

Billing later:
  Stripe or Razorpay

File storage later:
  Cloudinary or AWS S3
```

Environment variables:

```txt
PORT=
MONGODB_URI=
JWT_SECRET=
FRONTEND_URL=

GROQ_API_KEY=
GROQ_MODEL=

TAVILY_API_KEY=
BRAVE_SEARCH_API_KEY=
EXA_API_KEY=

FIRECRAWL_API_KEY=
REDIS_URL=

SMTP_HOST=
SMTP_PORT=
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=

STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=
```

===============================================================================
13. COLOR / UI DESIGN MAP
===============================================================================

Use a serious dark SaaS interface.

```txt
Background:
  #0F1117

Main surface:
  #161A22

Card/source surface:
  #1A1D27

Input surface:
  #202634

Border:
  #2B3241

Main text:
  #F3F5F7

Muted text:
  #A7ADB8

Subtle text:
  #737B8C

Accent:
  #20B2AA

Accent hover:
  #37C9C0

Danger:
  #EF4444
```

UI rules:

```txt
Do:
  search box first
  source cards visible
  inline citation badges
  skeleton loading
  dense useful layout
  responsive mobile layout

Avoid:
  marketing landing page as first screen
  too many decorative cards
  huge hero text inside app
  purple-heavy AI look
  hidden citations
```

