===============================================================================
15. SIMPLE MENTAL MODEL
===============================================================================

Think about the app in 4 layers:

```txt
1. UI Layer
   React pages and components.

2. API Layer
   Frontend services call backend routes.

3. Intelligence Layer
   Search + scrape + LLM + citations + streaming.

4. SaaS Layer
   Auth + history + usage + billing + settings.
```

Most important line:

```txt
The project becomes valuable when this works:

query -> search -> scrape -> AI answer -> citations -> stream -> save
```

